metadata.name: Praymatic
metadata.description:
Inspired by a Masterpiece of Chat By The Fireside
by Jean Leon Gerome's (1824-1904) 

Please zoom in to view all of the details; there are a lot of hidden old item here. Could you find them?

It took me more than 3 months of hard work to make this masterpiece, too many details and frame by frame I drew it. So I hope you can like it :D

Also you can find below some info for traditional animations, check it pls.
